//Inherited from Solar_Content_Abstract::fetchParts().//

<function>

access:   public

name: fetchParts

param: int, $parent_id

param: string, $where, NULL

param: array, $order, NULL

return: Solar_Sql_Rowset

</function>

Fetch the parts of a parent node ID.

* Parameters:

 * int //$parent_id//: The parent node ID.

 * string //$where//: Additional WHERE conditions.

 * array //$order//: Return in this order.

* Returns Solar_Sql_Rowset: A list of nodes that are children of the $parent_id node. The parts are not save()-able.